MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 5a3a40b1ee4441518f69c26c62cb3cde, type: 3}
  m_Name: Book_Level_03_Wolf_Intro
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueData
  dialogueId: book_level_03_wolf_intro
  lines:
  - speakerProfile: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 48ccf4465e991aa438795fe697d34f7a, type: 2}
    speakerName: Wolf
    text: Daughter of the steppe, your steps are light, but a heavy trail follows
      your people.
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 9a1139074231df44cb384f333e6482e1, type: 3}
  - speakerProfile: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6992f1ad55b7805439d6200abb695e15, type: 2}
    speakerName: Aisulu11
    text: I did not come to cut down trees, and I did not come to hunt. I am searching
      for the road to Umay and trying to understand where our guilt began.
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 39e15864a50fa1c4098c5a8759a13577, type: 3}
  - speakerProfile: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 48ccf4465e991aa438795fe697d34f7a, type: 2}
    speakerName: Wolf
    text: 'Guilt rarely begins with a loud cry. More often, it begins with a small
      thought: "This can be taken, because it does not speak."'
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 9a1139074231df44cb384f333e6482e1, type: 3}
  - speakerProfile: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6992f1ad55b7805439d6200abb695e15, type: 2}
    speakerName: Aisulu
    text: If the forest can remember, then fire can remember too. And if fire remembers,
      then Umay took it not out of cruelty, but out of pain.
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 39e15864a50fa1c4098c5a8759a13577, type: 3}
  - speakerProfile: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 48ccf4465e991aa438795fe697d34f7a, type: 2}
    speakerName: Wolf
    text: While I stand here, daughter of the steppe, you shall go no further. Not
      everyone who seeks Umay is worthy of approaching her fire.
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 9a1139074231df44cb384f333e6482e1, type: 3}
